channel.title: Help me out
channel.description:
When I try to use any web client, it works for about an hour then my screen goes white and will never load again. I can not launch any .bat files due to a error saying
[code]Windows can not find "C:/FILENAMEHERE" Make sure you typed it correctly.[/code]
All .jars make my computer lag extremely hard and never load.
I have the updated version of java.
